1260
01:23:39,760 --> 01:23:41,220
Em xuống đây!

1261
01:23:44,930 --> 01:23:46,140
Blu!

1262
01:23:46,430 --> 01:23:47,430
Không!

1263
01:24:02,990 --> 01:24:06,120
